52
00:02:36,920 --> 00:02:38,040
What a waste that we leave.

53
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,400
A pity?

54
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,360
You can go back.

55
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,680
There are snacks and a sofa.

56
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:43,680
You can sleep.

57
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:44,680
Don't say that.

58
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:45,400
If I go back,

59
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:47,040
where can you go so late at night?

60
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:48,920
You actually want to go back?

61
00:02:49,536 --> 00:02:50,040
No.

62
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:51,040
Why do you care where I go?

63
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:51,840
Wait.

64
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,360
Without me,

65
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,920
what if you run into bad people?

66
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:55,520
Right?

67
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:58,920
All you care about
is whether I run into bad people?

68
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:00,760
There's nothing else?

69
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:01,840
What else?

70
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:02,920
You...

71
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:07,040
Then where do we go?

72
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:07,840
We can't stroll

73
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,920
on the road all night.

74
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:13,280
I'm tired.

75
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,040
I'll stay here.

76
00:03:14,040 --> 00:03:14,920
I won't go anywhere.

77
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:19,000
This is the road.

78
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:20,400
What if a car comes over?

79
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:21,920
You will... Right?

80
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:23,200
Plus, it's cold at night.

81
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:24,120
I'm not wearing much.

82
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:24,640
I can't

83
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:25,760
magically produce a coat

84
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:27,640
for you to wear
like the male lead in a movie.

85
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:28,200
Wait.

86
00:03:29,480 --> 00:03:31,200
Don't you have hands
if you have no coat?

87
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,400
What should I do?

88
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:35,120
How about I do some Qigong for you?

89
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:39,360
Why would I ever know a fool like you?

90
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,480
Where are you going?

91
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:42,048
I...

92
00:03:43,480 --> 00:03:44,480
Why do you even care?

93
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,400
Don't be mad.

94
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:48,120
Right?

95
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:49,000
Stop following me.

96
00:03:49,920 --> 00:03:50,640
We can talk.

97
00:03:50,640 --> 00:03:52,360
Any issues can be solved.

98
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:58,000
Come in.

99
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:01,920
Why not mention this great place sooner?

100
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:04,000
We had nowhere else to go.

101
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:04,920
That's why we're here.

102
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:08,120
This place is good.

103
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:09,840
Don't stop it.

104
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:11,040
They are Mr. Feng's treasures.

105
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:12,560
If you break them, he won't spare me.

106
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:15,000
I won't touch them. I'll just look.

107
00:04:17,400 --> 00:04:18,560
You can use the laptop.

108
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:19,680
I'll go to sleep now.

109
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:20,640
Okay.

110
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:39,680
Chat with me for a while.

111
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:41,960
Aren't you sleepy?

112
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,400
I can talk when I'm sleepy.

113
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:46,240
Then let's chat.

114
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,240
Why do you make a movie?

115
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:51,680
For a dream.

116
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:56,680
How did you know my nickname is 'Dream'?

117
00:04:57,960 --> 00:04:58,640
Right.

118
00:04:58,960 --> 00:05:00,240
For the dream of my childhood.

119
00:05:01,520 --> 00:05:02,680
You have a conscience.

120
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:06,920
Daring to argue with me?

121
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:07,800
(Comments)

122
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:08,640
Take this.

123
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,360
Keep it down. I'm going to sleep.

124
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:16,080
Alright, I'll keep it down.

125
00:05:22,644 --> 00:05:23,456
(Each person understands the film
based on their own values.)

126
00:05:23,456 --> 00:05:24,256
(After reading your comment,
I find you very insightful.)

127
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:01,080
She's pretty from all angles.

128
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,520
It's a pity

129
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:04,680
that she is noisy.

130
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:36,520
Where are you going?

131
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:45,800
I'm hungry. I'm going to buy some food.

132
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:51,920
How about
buying two bottles of wine too?

133
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:05,680
He's sleeping so soundly.

134
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:08,960
He must have been tired.

135
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:13,240
Wake up.

136
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,120
Who are you?

137
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:19,520
I-I am Li Yanhao.

138
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,760
And s-she...

139
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:23,800
Where is she?

140
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:24,800
Tell me honestly.

141
00:08:24,960 --> 00:08:26,120
How did you get in?

142
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,920
I have checked just now.

143
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:29,680
Our company
is missing many valuable items.

144
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,240
Look at the camera.

145
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,240
Confess now.

146
00:08:32,800 --> 00:08:33,800
Wait... what is all this?

147
00:08:33,800 --> 00:08:35,680
I... I am not a thief.

148
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,800
Li Jiatong brought me here yesterday.

149
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,120
Don't you know Li Jiatong?

150
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:40,920
Who is Li Jiatong?

151
00:08:41,680 --> 00:08:43,040
I don't know Li Jiatong.

152
00:08:43,560 --> 00:08:44,680
How could that be? I'm not...

153
00:08:44,680 --> 00:08:45,560
Alright, Mr. Feng.

154
00:08:46,040 --> 00:08:46,920
Stop teasing him.

155
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,240
Let me tease him a bit.

156
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:52,360
Give it to me.

157
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,240
Tell me.

158
00:08:54,680 --> 00:08:56,360
Why did you film me sneakily last night?

159
00:08:58,560 --> 00:09:00,360
I thought you looked pretty.

160
00:09:01,920 --> 00:09:02,680
You did think so?

161
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:06,000
That's more like it.

162
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,040
Let me introduce them.

163
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,800
They're the people that we film with.

164
00:09:08,800 --> 00:09:09,480
Mr. Feng.

165
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:10,920
Big Head.

166
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:12,920
Blackie.

167
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:15,040
And he is...

168
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:16,040
Li Yanhao, right?

169
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,800
He caused trouble last time.

170
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:18,440
Right.

171
00:09:18,920 --> 00:09:19,880
We all know him.

172
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:21,120
We all know the thing

173
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,120
between you two.

174
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:23,560
What thing between us?

175
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,120
Alright, don't stand there.

176
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:29,800
Let's go.

177
00:09:29,800 --> 00:09:30,480
Where to?

178
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:31,720
Back to school.

179
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:33,560
We stayed at Mr. Feng's for a night.

180
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:34,600
They still have to work.

181
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,440
Don't disturb them.

182
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:37,320
Mr. Feng,

183
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:39,040
